metadata.name: Mother Earth
metadata.description:
Mother Earth
This is a painting by Allison S. Requenes painted in 2021 with water paints, inspired by the beauty of nature, the harmony between animals, trees and the earth, a splendid pose of a tree with a female figure and birds that they delight in its beauty and coexist with each other in eternal peace.

I thank Allison for this wonderful representation of Mother Earth!
